Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来我的一个任务也完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.73,0:00:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的任务就是等他复活了…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沉住气  夏美姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.32,0:00:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你可是作战的关键啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:00:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说没问题的…但并不是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.28,0:01:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我不再加把劲的话  是不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说  的确是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成功率会下降的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我不会勉强你做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.94,0:01:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别太在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.53,0:01:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.82,0:01:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.55,0:01:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的  难得当一回主角啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.02,0:01:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.18,0:01:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.72,0:01:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,犬上小太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,贝…贝同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,贝阿托莉克斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,裕…裕奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,震耳欲聋的雷之神枪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\pos(320,436)\fe1\fnMonotype Corsiva}L?gjarn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.55,0:03:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.48,0:03:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,主角  你太慢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你赢了  涅吉君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…那是…
