Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\pos(320,436)}Code of the Lifemaker
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后之键
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\pos(320,436)}Great Grand Masterkey
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我以黄昏的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,造物主的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,始祖阿玛提鲁的末裔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.48,0:05:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜·维斯佩里娜·提奥塔纳希亚·安提奥菲歇尔之名下令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让世界恢复原状吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:30.39,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}在那之后  又过了几个月…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人分别再做20个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:06:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这看上去像是涅吉老师要毕业了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的确呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,班级名册呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是涅吉弟弟刚来这学校时努力写下的备注呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是发生了不少事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是平时不好好整理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才会变成这样一团糟的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉  学园长叫你去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他让你立刻去学园长室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么了呢  学园长会突然叫你去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是关于明天的毕业典礼的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:07:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  说不定真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这班级完全是一点进展都没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（古菲开始抢扎吉的饭碗了吗…）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总…总之我先去看看吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师好失落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会被学园长训了掉眼泪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错呢  好久没看到涅吉弟弟的哭像了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拍个特写做成毕业相集的封面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么干  就这么干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神来啊  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有我跟着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢了  卡莫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法世界那边怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  复原进展比想象得还要顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊  你们做得真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了有大家鼎力相助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且总算是赶上毕业典礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对了  关于这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…毕业典礼的话  现在非常顺利地在…进行着准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嬉闹着的小姐们的景象仿佛就在眼前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不  大概…很顺利…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是关于毕业典礼的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来听听看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师在被训吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:09:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚的话是真的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不不  不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,详细说明下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说  就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然至今为止涅吉弟弟跟我们中的许多人签下了暂定契约
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是暂定契约的有效期快过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  就快毕业了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本来  魔法使的搭档就只有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要成为涅吉老师所希望的「魔法使的指导者」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\pos(430,436)}Magister Magi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎就得在明天前选出一个正式的  而非暂定契约的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么没有被选中的人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暂定契约就会解除
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不光是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有被选上的人  关于魔法的记忆似乎也会被消除的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆会被消除吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟老师度过的日子会被忘却
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这么回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:10:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:11:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是为了保护魔法世界的必要法则
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既便如此  也是令人悲伤的法则呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  就算现在没有签订暂定契约的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以被选作正式契约的搭档的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（配角们的逆袭）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:15.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  全员都有着相同的几率被选中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到  到现在还能够一下获取女主角的宝座啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（ごめん、お前は無理）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看  看上去好难…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这时刻我等了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就是释放爱的力量  俘获涅吉老师芳心的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这大逆转的FLAG  就由我来竖给你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好像燃起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.32,0:11:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  跟毕业无比相称的热闹气氛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一说  感觉像是突然绽放又一下子凋谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:12:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宛如樱花一样的活动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓制造最后的回忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我兴奋起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  这样的话就大家一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,取名为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「获取正式契约  在毕业典礼上成为涅吉老师的Only One」大作战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  大家在干什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（噢噢，路人NO.1突击）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫雪广绫香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫雪广绫香哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我知道的说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好狡猾  班长偷跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（路人众突袭）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,衣  衣服被…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还真做得出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（主角表示没有压力233）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,于是谁都没能使出必杀一击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啪地一下抓住涅吉老师心…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种手感呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且涅吉老师有一种心不在焉的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的确呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  班长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天来不来我家住一晚？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行的话  木乃香和樱咲同学也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,突然间怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么理由啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难得一次也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,木乃香  没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  这样一来木乃香大小姐的房间里不就只剩涅吉老师一个人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的  今晚他有很多事情要考虑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉也是希望一个人待着的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那明日菜  去通知下涅吉弟弟去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,OK  我去去就来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里站着别动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜来找你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,木乃香同学有什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听不清她在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我和木乃香去班长家住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊  你要好好想清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于正式契约的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会说谁都不选吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好选出一个人哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为你的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学  你知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  班级里所有人都知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今天大家才那么奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说你太迟钝了啊  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是早就知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（马后炮主义者）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  大家都已经雀跃不已了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到了明天  没被选上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会把魔法的存在和魔法世界里发生的事都忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:16:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我也没法想象呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐头  等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐头的记忆是不会消失的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为啊  大姐头虽说是暂定契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但也和别人不一样  本就是魔法世界的住人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还有魔法无效化能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\pos(340,436)}Magic Cancel
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌  我以为我会和大家一样忘掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢  怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（这可爱的东西是啥？你确定她是明日菜？）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  木乃香大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非明日菜同学就算没有成为正式契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆也不会消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  明日菜同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,决定了  我也忘了它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不公平嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会想办法忘掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想办法…你是打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说  就是把魔法无效化的无效化能力给消除掉什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\pos(245,436)}Magic Cancel
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要去多想什么有的没的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管结果如何  大家都会接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题  明天我肯定会选出一名搭档来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  这就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀  他这不都明白的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枫同学  古老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,据说到了明天就会忘却掉很多记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那在这之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望最后来交次手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找你很久了  枫！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你没忘记约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才是决胜的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在吗？  再等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,时间只到明天为止的事  大家都是一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师  行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么行不行的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.86,0:19:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  在陪枫过招之后就是涅吉老师您了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我的对手就是涅吉小弟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事情变得好玩起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（阿澄佳奈的声音听着我想笑怎么办……）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正式…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,显现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\pos(320,436)}Adeat
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.64,0:19:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请  请等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  涅吉小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请认真陪我交手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不记得我教给你的是这么软弱的战斗方式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.36,0:20:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是看不起你师傅了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我就不留情  全力以赴上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉小弟也拿出全力攻过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,显现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\pos(320,436)}Adeat
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（破衣的实力一如既往……）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:18.34,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（魔法使与小小的愿望）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.98,0:21:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟涅吉老师的故乡应该很像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到了明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和香？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夕映
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.42,0:21:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊  和香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.58,0:22:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢了  夕映
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏你我才能提前结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.75,0:22:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.05,0:22:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（我说这奇怪的POSE难道又是新房的嗜好？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.02,0:22:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,显现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.02,0:22:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\pos(320,436)}Adeat
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看吧  和香
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是真名  刚刚那下还真稍微有点危险
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.95,0:23:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两位
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.56,0:23:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到…到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.69,0:23:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是最后的交锋了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.47,0:23:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.62,0:23:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为到了明天  可能就什么都不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.72,0:24:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在还记得涅吉小弟  想认真打上一次
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.83,0:24:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到了明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.69,0:24:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枫忍法  十六分身
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.09,0:24:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种小把戏对我可没用
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.30,0:24:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本体  在那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.14,0:24:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.20,0:24:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天狗的隐蓑！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.58,0:24:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枫忍法  四重分身
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.41,0:24:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,胧十字
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.68,0:24:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真名同学
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.13,0:24:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我输了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.25,0:24:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  千钧一发的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.23,0:25:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是输给了你对于涅吉老师的那份情感了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.98,0:25:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…说不定就是如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.25,0:25:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.89,0:25:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.77,0:25:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  涅吉小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.80,0:25:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.35,0:25:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今你该不会拒战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.15,0:25:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.68,0:25:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甲贺中忍  长濑枫  出战！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.11,0:25:53.45,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（梵文：不动明王真言  不动一字咒）
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.11,0:25:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,南无·三曼多·伐折罗·赧·含
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.34,0:25:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,缚锁爆炎阵
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.96,0:26:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Sinistra Emisa Stagnet{\r}\N左腕解放固定
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.50,0:26:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}ΚΙΛΙΠΛ　ΑΣΤΡΑΠΗ{\r}\N千之雷
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.78,0:26:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Dextera Emisa Stagnet{\r}\N右腕解放固定
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.14,0:26:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}ΚΙΛΙΠΛ　ΑΣΤΡΑΠΗ{\r}\N千之雷
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.61,0:26:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Duabus Complexio{\r}\N双腕掌握！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.22,0:26:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Pro Armatione{\r}\N术式兵装
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.91,0:26:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}η αστραπη ηυπερ ουρανου μεγα δυναμενε II{\r}\N雷天大壮II
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.98,0:26:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}ταστλαπα ηυπερ ουρανου μεγα δυναμενε{\r}\N雷天双壮
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.82,0:26:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还真没想到你会使用这个咒文啊  涅吉小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.39,0:26:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我要全力应对枫同学的这份感情
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.80,0:27:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完败…了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（S体型的回避加成吗……
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.49,0:27:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.83,0:27:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然知道会是这样  不过没想到居然完全没法抗衡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.55,0:27:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.41,0:27:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,变强了呢  涅吉小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.29,0:27:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.74,0:27:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你没受伤吧  枫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.11,0:27:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.93,0:27:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.70,0:27:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真名也是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.51,0:27:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.95,0:27:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.21,0:27:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎游刃有余啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.77,0:27:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.61,0:27:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,挺混乱的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.27,0:27:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  似乎没事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.97,0:27:59.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,消去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.97,0:27:59.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\pos(320,436)}Abeat
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.72,0:28:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师是个十分出色的人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.85,0:28:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夕映？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.27,0:28:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和香会喜欢上他也不难理解
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.14,0:28:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  我会喜欢上他也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.70,0:28:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夕映…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.16,0:28:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没办法想象现在这样的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.30,0:28:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为我一辈子不会去喜欢上一个男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.06,0:28:38.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.38,0:28:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.71,0:28:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会有能够这样谈论恋爱话题的朋友在
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.81,0:28:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到身边一直会有朋友在
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.25,0:28:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是难以置信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.85,0:29:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能够这样在一起  可能也是因为同识这份恋心的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.89,0:29:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我能和夕映喜欢上一样的人  真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（3P flag威武！）
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.41,0:29:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能跟和香喜欢上一样的人  同样也是我的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.21,0:29:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果明天我们中的某个人被选上的话
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.03,0:29:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.43,0:29:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有这么开心的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.04,0:29:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.77,0:29:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.36,0:29:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.23,0:29:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和香同学  夕映同学
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.65,0:29:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真能干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.71,0:29:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.76,0:29:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.45,0:29:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.01,0:29:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.10,0:29:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.52,0:30:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好闲  天还没亮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.42,0:30:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,数据保存暂且算是完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.98,0:30:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.89,0:30:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.00,0:30:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使做这种小动作也是没有意义的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.57,0:30:26.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也是这么觉得的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.80,0:30:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为茶茶丸无论如何都要我这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.85,0:30:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.08,0:30:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.61,0:30:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.74,0:30:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.96,0:30:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之前听到她恋爱的时候我也吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.28,0:30:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真有意思啊  没想到居然能发展出「爱情」
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.04,0:30:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.56,0:30:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爱是指…？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.41,0:30:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是茶茶丸现在所做的行为的原动力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.66,0:30:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爱啦  勇气啦  还有回忆之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.36,0:31:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不相信这些看不到的非科学的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.88,0:31:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～原来是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.84,0:31:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.38,0:31:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,主人  如果明天早上记忆失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.08,0:31:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这份爱还会保留着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.61,0:31:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.71,0:31:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,过去那小子找到了你的灵魂不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.03,0:31:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.93,0:31:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就让他帮你把爱也找回来好了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.56,0:31:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算失去一次也没什么可着急的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.60,0:31:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为人类会无数次地爱上别人的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.65,0:31:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.80,0:31:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀  居然连依文都这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.44,0:31:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.65,0:31:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  什么都没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.43,0:32:07.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮我拿给夏美吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.22,0:32:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？为什么要我来？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.43,0:32:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.55,0:32:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.28,0:32:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.24,0:32:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千鹤姐给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.12,0:32:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.69,0:32:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏美姐姐  好像一脸深沉的表情呐
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.66,0:32:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想大家都怎么样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.23,0:32:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.80,0:32:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被涅吉弟弟选中的人以外都会失去关于魔法的记忆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.16,0:32:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定都心跳不已  睡不着觉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.13,0:32:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算是…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.07,0:32:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千鹤姐也会忘记的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.57,0:33:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和小太郎相遇的事情也都…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.20,0:33:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得夏美姐姐的记忆是不会消失的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.47,0:33:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为和我签订了暂定契约
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.82,0:33:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.07,0:33:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我一个人记得的话  总觉得就不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.83,0:33:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？  你说的含义我不太明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.12,0:33:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.14,0:33:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我一个人拥有记忆的话  就不止是记忆了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.71,0:33:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为千鹤姐还有涅吉  以及大家都记得的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.42,0:33:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才能以回忆的形式保存下来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.52,0:33:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是的  为什么你不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.41,0:33:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.31,0:33:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.29,0:33:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说不清楚  就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.96,0:33:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.45,0:33:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会有这么悲哀的规则存在
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.94,0:33:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.72,0:33:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是以后肯定会因此获得什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.32,0:33:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.07,0:33:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说  这样脑袋开动全力思考之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.26,0:34:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,担心朋友的感觉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.83,0:34:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.30,0:34:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.29,0:34:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成为帮所爱的人寻找现在能做到的事的契机之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.92,0:34:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概就是告诉人们这种事情的规则吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.73,0:34:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.28,0:34:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  涅吉所用的魔法是不会让人变得不幸的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.02,0:34:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.19,0:34:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.61,0:34:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你也不必哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.26,0:34:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌  小太郎你好像太得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.76,0:34:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说那么成熟的话
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.38,0:34:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是夏美姐姐你说寂寞的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.23,0:34:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡冷掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.04,0:35:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让千鹤姐再来一杯就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.20,0:35:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（噢噢噢噢！上啊，极意·千鹤流双葱爆菊杀！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.15,0:35:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好丰盛
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.41,0:35:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去好可口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.98,0:35:26.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来  尽管吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.36,0:35:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.49,0:35:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  很豪华呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.36,0:35:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这点程度怎么能少
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.36,0:35:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可是前夜祭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.33,0:35:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前夜祭？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.76,0:35:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是提前庆祝我和涅吉老师订立正式契约
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.74,0:35:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正餐之后是甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.59,0:35:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后是茶会
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.06,0:35:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  夜宵我也准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.96,0:35:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到明早为止  就请安心享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.54,0:35:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要一晚上吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.32,0:35:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,班长你心神不宁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.85,0:35:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.47,0:36:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到了明天记忆消失了的话  会很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.80,0:36:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今天才让我们来你这住的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.76,0:36:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才…才没有这种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.45,0:36:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是觉得像明日菜这样吵闹的人在涅吉老师身边
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.80,0:36:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会打搅他的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.47,0:36:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的确呢  我不在他身边比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.71,0:36:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说得好像别人的事一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.40,0:36:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.29,0:36:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学不在意谁被选上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.95,0:36:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…书店她们要是被选上的话
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.01,0:36:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会很开心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.33,0:36:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜没想过自己会被选上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.01,0:36:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.70,0:36:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  明日菜的可能性也是很高的说
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.29,0:36:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.22,0:36:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是不可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.96,0:36:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是相当困难的选择呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.88,0:36:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法整理自己的想法  陷入混乱觉得怎么都行的涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.91,0:36:58.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后…一不小心…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.98,0:37:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就作出了个最简单方便的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.34,0:37:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.01,0:37:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.29,0:37:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等到他注意的时候早就木已成舟
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.06,0:37:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要一辈子照料这个无法无天的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.23,0:37:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最终身心俱疲再起不能了…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.20,0:37:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,班长！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.29,0:37:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是说了真相而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.38,0:37:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  你们两位…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.55,0:37:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.75,0:37:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好漂亮的满月
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.14,0:37:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小刹  出去赏下月不
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.79,0:37:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快来～
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.43,0:37:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.80,0:37:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这还真是本人一生的最高杰作了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.02,0:37:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天醒来后如果还记得的话
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.41,0:38:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就送给涅吉弟弟当礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.01,0:38:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说笑了  怎么说我都不可能被选中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.92,0:38:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算记忆失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.05,0:38:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能画出这样的漫画也不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.89,0:38:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,主页好久没更新了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.63,0:38:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就是最后了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.37,0:38:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这么做也是没有意义的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.30,0:38:57.68,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}大家好  都还过得好吗\N很久没更新了呢  大家是不是久等了\N这是我非常中意的COS装哦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.53,0:39:06.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天住在这里真的没关系吗  明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.50,0:39:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.48,0:39:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不在他身边的话  涅吉老师可能真的会选别人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.33,0:39:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经被选中很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.73,0:39:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经被选择得够多了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.03,0:39:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既便如此  果然我还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.71,0:39:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜同学  我还是认为你该被选中
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.87,0:39:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,班长…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.25,0:39:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来明天也会是个好天气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.49,0:39:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有点困了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.70,0:39:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小刹  差不多该去睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.14,0:39:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,木乃香大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.59,0:39:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.42,0:40:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和小姐已经签订了暂定契约
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.65,0:40:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以即使涅吉老师选择了别人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.00,0:40:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也一定不会有什么变化
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.00,0:40:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.99,0:40:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能够承受住其他人不再记得魔法的这种日常生活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.99,0:40:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.19,0:40:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多数没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.79,0:40:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有小刹在我身边嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.30,0:40:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且就算记忆没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.52,0:40:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是最爱的同班同学这事是不会变的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.48,0:40:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.75,0:40:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  小刹  摆出这样表情的话
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.50,0:40:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上就会梦见很恐怖的梦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.25,0:40:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笑一笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.25,0:40:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,木乃香…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.38,0:40:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小…大小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.17,0:41:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊  大家愿意就这样迎来明天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.16,0:41:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到了明天我们就会忘记关于魔法的事了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.39,0:41:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.63,0:41:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么什么都不做  你们能安心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.70,0:41:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.37,0:41:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就做点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.24,0:41:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.48,0:41:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚也才刚开始嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.89,0:41:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么就睡了的话太浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.17,0:41:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听上去好棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.59,0:41:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…要做些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.72,0:41:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起晚上的事  那自然就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.64,0:41:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夜袭！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.08,0:41:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不错嘛  你说呢  晶
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.63,0:41:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.84,0:41:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正基本到了明天早上大部分都会失去记忆的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.69,0:42:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后就…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.85,0:42:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.07,0:42:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这么说定了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.70,0:42:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,扎吉和美空也会去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.44,0:42:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  反正我闲着
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.39,0:42:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我去
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.04,0:42:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.25,0:42:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那既然决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.40,0:42:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就彻彻底底
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.18,0:42:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放手洗个干净
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.98,0:42:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是第一次给人洗那种地方啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.46,0:42:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呜…已经嫁不出去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（堀江您老的声音还是那么威武啊……）
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.73,0:42:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,裕奈你不去见下明石老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.21,0:42:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.51,0:42:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…到了明天的话
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.44,0:42:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该说只是回到从前了而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.91,0:42:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸和妈妈的事情  也已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.70,0:42:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或者说我已经理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.02,0:42:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.10,0:43:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  裕奈你这么想就行
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.72,0:43:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.28,0:43:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风香和史伽
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.82,0:43:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有小五也在
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.20,0:43:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒的味道  那是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.39,0:43:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我为涅吉老师准备的夜宵
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.40,0:43:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.74,0:43:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正好啊  不都说饿着肚子打不了仗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.01,0:43:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不是说了这是给涅吉老师的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.60,0:43:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  还有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.18,0:43:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是小五
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.24,0:43:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.08,0:43:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论哪个都那么闪耀  都那么漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.61,0:43:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.23,0:43:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只能选择一个吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.17,0:43:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有够为难的  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.13,0:43:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.13,0:43:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,脑袋里乱作一团了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.40,0:44:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  必须得好好考虑才行
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.74,0:44:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.53,0:44:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  说不定是对我们所有人的试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.99,0:44:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  为什么夜袭你们还要使用卡片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.85,0:44:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这可能是最后一次了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.27,0:44:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爽快地用次魔法夜袭去
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.55,0:44:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夜…夜袭可不是这样的东西啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.00,0:44:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正是最后一次了  干得华丽点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.37,0:45:01.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我是不参加的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.80,0:45:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家请加油
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.39,0:45:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看见了  涅吉老师的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.85,0:45:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.03,0:45:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.50,0:45:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会输给你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.67,0:45:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.06,0:45:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等下  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.97,0:45:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么干的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.64,0:45:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  干得过火了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.14,0:45:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉弟弟  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.27,0:45:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  涅吉不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.53,0:45:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜和木乃香也不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.44,0:45:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难…难道说被吹飞到外面了…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.76,0:45:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.00,0:46:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.72,0:46:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥  这可不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.97,0:46:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太快了  来得太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.28,0:46:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,学园长  师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.93,0:46:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来了吗  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.43,0:46:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.58,0:46:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,火星居然那么大了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.58,0:46:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为在接近地球了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.83,0:46:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.03,0:46:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么了啊  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.65,0:46:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  这都是我的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.69,0:46:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事  涅吉君
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.52,0:46:54.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现实世界和魔法世界进行融合的话
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.22,0:46:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就能创造出谁都不会受伤  什么都不会破坏的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.61,0:47:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是乌托邦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.28,0:47:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乌托邦？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.72,0:47:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么  听起来好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（虽不明但觉厉233
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.12,0:47:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  但在火星的周围有着保护自己的强大结界
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.78,0:47:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以大哥才花了30年思考解除结界并进行融合的方案吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.54,0:47:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是魔法世界的落下比预想得要快吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.57,0:47:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.64,0:47:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…这样下去如果碰撞的话  会怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.16,0:47:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论哪个世界都不会安然无恙…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.99,0:47:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.49,0:47:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉  没什么办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.81,0:47:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能破坏那个结界的话  就…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.25,0:47:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  以我的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.47,0:47:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.77,0:48:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么呢  还不快提升魔法的强度
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.29,0:48:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  完全止不住
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.72,0:48:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,超鬼激距离炮·拉坎冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.34,0:48:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊  这么做的话地球会…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.52,0:49:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这还真是不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.30,0:49:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有魔法使的指导者的力量的话  就能做到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.30,0:49:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\pos(215,436)}Magister Magi
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.47,0:49:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.74,0:49:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  用魔法使的指导者的魔力的话  的确有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.74,0:49:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\pos(240,436)}Magister Magi
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.04,0:49:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,与吸收原初的魔法使的攻击时候的小子的力量基本持平
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.28,0:49:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.57,0:49:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是与那时候一样的力量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.21,0:49:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.52,0:49:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就赶紧进行吧  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.50,0:49:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.81,0:49:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么「哎」啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.11,0:49:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你赶紧选择一个人签订正式契约  成为魔法使的指导者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.11,0:49:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\pos(473,436)}Magister Magi
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.08,0:49:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.12,0:49:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎——？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.53,0:49:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不必那么惊讶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.50,0:49:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,除了涅吉弟弟以外也没人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.77,0:49:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.29,0:49:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  既然明白了  那就快行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.27,0:50:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  已经不是能够拖到明天天亮的事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.56,0:50:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.65,0:50:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在发什么呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.32,0:50:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快作出选择吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.02,0:50:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  请赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.75,0:50:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.37,0:50:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么但是
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.72,0:50:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.91,0:50:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.23,0:50:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.54,0:50:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,选择其中一位…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.59,0:50:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  涅吉君
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.22,0:50:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只能…选一人？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.79,0:50:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.58,0:50:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天所在的世界  今天这样的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.92,0:50:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是依靠这里在场的所有人才得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.24,0:50:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  还有不在这里的人  魔法世界的伙伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.09,0:50:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以及期盼着同样未来的人们  是靠大家才取得的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.71,0:50:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.02,0:51:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.62,0:51:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在一定要作出选择的话
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.43,0:51:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…选择我所有的学生们
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.77,0:51:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.63,0:51:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  涅吉君
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.39,0:51:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.38,0:51:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.13,0:51:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三下五除二地解决掉它去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.00,0:52:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  那就30人份契约  开始咯
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.83,0:52:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Pactio{\r}\N契约
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.76,0:52:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉  交给你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.23,0:52:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.66,0:52:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Spiritus pactionis qui praestani
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.81,0:52:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Addo evocation, ne amo respondeo
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.05,0:52:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Ego, rego universi, in treme peto amicitia
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.95,0:52:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Me nunquam adamanti, immortalis, magnifici animi iungo
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.63,0:53:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Veram pactio{\r}\N正式契约
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.73,0:53:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.22,0:53:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然一下子让这么多人的正式契约都成功了？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.53,0:53:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.56,0:53:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.65,0:53:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,星星们哟
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.82,0:53:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.82,0:54:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么大的结界  真的能打破吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.98,0:54:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,光是破坏掉是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.68,0:54:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,解除结界  并释放让火星和地球融合的魔法才行
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.24,0:54:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.51,0:54:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相当困难的咒文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.24,0:54:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.52,0:54:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  应该是必须得做到
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.97,0:54:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有什么地方是结界的弱点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.51,0:54:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.62,0:54:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对着那里使用魔法的话  就能用最小的能量破坏结界
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.87,0:54:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对魔法世界也不会造成伤害了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.52,0:54:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能用夕映的道具卡来找出那个弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.69,0:54:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  我来试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.71,0:54:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Adeat{\r}\N显现
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.41,0:54:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Orbis Sensualium Pictus{\r}\N世界图绘
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.03,0:54:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了  在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.01,0:54:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  那大家一起上了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.13,0:54:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Adeat{\r}\N显现
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.25,0:55:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Iris Tormentum{\r}\N七色手枪
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.64,0:55:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Vor So Kratiker Sokratiker
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.94,0:55:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Unus Fulgor{\r}\N将黑夜撕裂的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.31,0:55:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Concidens Noctem{\r}\N一束光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.89,0:55:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}in Mea Manu Ens{\r}\N汇聚至我的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.49,0:55:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Inimicum Edat{\r}\N吞噬敌人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.37,0:55:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Fulguratio Albicans{\r}\N白色闪电
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.99,0:55:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Adeat{\r}\N显现
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.15,0:55:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Liberum Lemniscus{\r}\N自在缎带
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.62,0:55:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Frango Stipes{\r}\N粉碎棍棒
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.97,0:55:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Bombus Globus{\r}\N爆弹之球
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.47,0:55:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.22,0:55:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Adeat{\r}\N显现
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.48,0:55:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神珍铁自在棍
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.43,0:55:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.42,0:55:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Adeat{\r}\N显现
